<h1>Edit Wiki</h1>

<div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-4">
        <p>Thank you for contributing to Interstellar Wiki! Here are some guidelines:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Wikis will be nested by arch-topics.</li>            <!-- to do: create these arch-topics and nest wikis within them, as well as display in wiki/index.-->
            <li>Please try and source all claims.</li>
            <li>See the styleguide page, for more info.</li>         <!-- to do: create a styleguide page outlining the vision of interstellar wiki pages. -->
        </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-8">
        <%= render partial: 'form', locals: { wiki: @wiki } %>
    </div>
</div>
<% if current_user.admin? || current_user == @wiki.user %>
    <%= link_to "Manage Collaborators", wiki_collaborators_path(@wiki) %>
<% elsif @wiki.users.include?(current_user) %>
    <%= link_to "View Collaborators", wiki_collaborators_path(@wiki) %>
<% end %>
